    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Affordable project car or basic transportation for the right buyer. This vehicle is in poor condition and shows clear wear inside and out, so it should be expected to need repairs and ongoing attention. That said, it could still be a solid opportunity for someone handy, looking for parts, or needing a budget-friendly car with potential.",
