      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Exceptionally clean mint-condition example that shows outstanding care throughout. The body, paint, trim, and interior all present beautifully, with the kind of freshness and overall finish buyers hope to find in a top-quality car. This is not a project or fixer-upper\u2014expect a very well-kept vehicle that stands out for its condition and would satisfy a buyer looking for one of the nicer examples on the market.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer seeking affordable transportation, a project car, or a dependable extra set of wheels. It shows clear signs of age and wear, but it offers strong value for the money and a straightforward opportunity for someone who appreciates an honest, usable vehicle at an accessible price point.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left in it for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option that could make a great runabout, first car, or little project for someone handy. It has the kind of character you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle, and at this price, there\u2019s real value for anyone who wants simple, affordable motoring without spending a fortune. If you want something approachable, practical, and priced to sell, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget driver/project with plenty of life left in the powertrain. Advertised in poor condition due to cosmetic wear, age-related faults, and general rough-around-the-edges presentation, but it still offers dependable mechanical basics and a strong-running engine that pulls well through the rev range. Chassis feels planted, steering is direct, and it\u2019s a great candidate for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on weekend fixer without spending big money up front. If you know how to turn a wrench, there\u2019s real value here.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap entry car. Honest poor-condition deal with solid value for the money. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real story, real presence, and the kind of character you just don\u2019t get from something forgettable. It\u2019s the sort of ride that still turns heads in the driveway and offers a great opportunity for someone who appreciates honest metal, weekend tinkering, or simply wants affordable wheels with soul. Whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly daily, a backup vehicle, or a project with plenty of promise, this one brings personality in spades and the chance to make it your own.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical option for a buyer who wants affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It offers straightforward value with an honest presentation and plenty of potential for someone ready to put it to work. A smart low-cost entry point for commuting, backup use, or hands-on ownership.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
